#: ../../source/enterprise.rst:2
msgid "Official support"
msgstr "官方支持"

#: ../../source/enterprise.rst:4
msgid ""
"Our goal is to ensure that your developers are successful and productive "
"with Nest as well as other, modern technologies. With official support, "
"you can get expert help straight from Nest core team. We provide "
"dedicated **technical support**, advice on best practices (and design "
"decisions), PR reviews, and team augmentation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/enterprise.rst:45
msgid "First-hand access"
msgstr "第一手访问"

#: ../../source/enterprise.rst:47
msgid ""
"Direct communication channel will boost team velocity, giving a quick "
"access to discuss and solve problems."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/enterprise.rst:51
msgid "Workshops and trainings"
msgstr "研讨会和培训"

#: ../../source/enterprise.rst:53
msgid ""
"We provide solid kick-off training as well as more advanced ones that "
"help teams understand Nest deeply. We offer on-site workshops and remote "
"intensive session which give you the fastest way to get familiar with "
"Nest ecosystem."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/enterprise.rst:59
msgid "Contact"
msgstr "联系"

#: ../../source/enterprise.rst:61
msgid ""
"Let’s talk how we can help you become successful with Nest: "
"support@nestjs.com"
msgstr ""

